abstract: Unidentified Connecticut woman who became pregnant during trip to Central America is found to have Zika virus, becoming third Connecticut resident to receive Zika diagnosis.
lead_paragraph: The woman, the third resident of the state to receive a Zika diagnosis, became ill with a fever and a rash while traveling to Central America about a month ago.

headline.main: Pregnant Connecticut Woman Is Found to Have Zika Virus
